<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: Paladin/Necro</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Heresy">Heresy</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 4:39 p.m. 17/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Paladin/Necro<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/rallos_zek.cgi?read=4" TARGET=_self>Paladin/Necro</A> (Sudoxe)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>> Hail to thee all. I have some question to

<BR>&gt; "high" levels players, because i
<BR>&gt; cannot choose between a Dwarf Paladin and a
<BR>&gt; Gnome Necromancer...
<P>&gt; If you can answer to ONLY ONE question, just
<BR>&gt; do it, im sure it would help me a lot !!
<BR>&gt; Thank you very much...
<P>&gt; About Paladins:
<P>&gt; 1) Paladins have the spell Blindness, at
<BR>&gt; level 9. How long does it last ? Is it easy
<BR>&gt; to resist (--> Duels) ?
<P>Resisting spells is dependant on your Magic resist and the level of the caster vs. the level of the castee. It lasts a variable time, but ~15-20 seconds.
<P>&gt; 2) Same question, but for Root, level 22.
<BR>&gt; How long does it last and is it easy to
<BR>&gt; resist ?
<P>Same answer, Root can last quite a long time though. But when you cast another offensive spell against the rooted target the root is broken. If you travel with a buddy that does the Root and you attack with ranged weapon it will be very effective.
<P>&gt; 3) Did anyone of you found NPCs selling high
<BR>&gt; level paladins spells stunning (like Smite
<BR>&gt; or Holy Might of the cleric's spells) ?
<P>You can find most Paladin spells in the Paladin guild, you can also buy them from th Cleric guild. Not sure if any stun.
<P>&gt; 4) Any infos on the incredible Holy Swords,
<BR>&gt; most powerfull swords of norrath, paladins
<BR>&gt; only ?
<P>Almost all classes are going to have "super weapons" the best weapon is NOT a Paladin sword, there are equally powerful weapons for most warrior classes.
<P>&gt; 5) Are the AR spells of the Paladins good
<BR>&gt; for him or really too weak ?
<P>Any extra Armor/Health helps.
<P>&gt; About Necromancers:
<P>&gt; 1) Did anyone of you found NPCs selling high
<BR>&gt; level that Root ? Or Stun ?
<P>Necros get Root at very high level (39th I think) not sure about stunning spells
<P>&gt; 2) Is Cancel Magic spell destroying easely
<BR>&gt; the DOT spells like Heart Flutter ?
<P>Dispeling magic is much the same as resisting, it depends on the caster/castee levels.
<P>&gt; 3) Are the AR necro spells good ?
<P>Yes, very good AR/HP/Magic Resist
<P>&gt; 4) Any good hight level spells, or direct
<BR>&gt; damages spells ?
<P>They have awesome high level DOT (damage over time) spells: Boil Blood, Disease, Poison, etc.
<P>&gt; I really cannot make up my mind... If you
<BR>&gt; have any tips or ideas about what i should
<BR>&gt; choose, just tell me...
<P>&gt; THANK YOU VERY MUCH !
<P>&gt; Sincerely, Sudoxe
<P>Either should be a good class, with the Necro you are going to have both PC's and NPC against you. So, the life of the Paladin might be a little easier.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
